Subject: Issue with Self service portal - Owner is unable to import Excel sheet with user ID's
Description: shared folder owner tried to import the users list with Excel format, It pops up error: "Some users could not found". when we click Yes to read those users in order to remove them from the list, it pops up window with unreadable format. please find the screenshot attached
